#: src/components/modals/UserSettingsModal/Privacy.tsx:132
msgid "When on, anyone with your Quorum address can see your display name, avatar, and bio, even outside the Spaces you share. Useful when someone DMs you and you want them to recognize who you are. Off by default."
msgstr "Ko je vklopljeno, lahko vsakdo z vašim naslovom Quorum vidi vaše prikazno ime, avatar in biografijo, tudi zunaj Prostorov, ki jih delite. Uporabno, ko vam nekdo pošlje zasebno sporočilo in želite, da prepozna, kdo ste. Privzeto izklopljeno."

#: src/components/modals/UserSettingsModal/Privacy.tsx:250
msgid "When on, everyone in a Space channel sees when you're typing, and you see when they're typing."
msgstr "Ko je vklopljeno, vsi v kanalu Prostora vidijo, kdaj tipkate, in vi vidite, kdaj tipkajo oni."

#: src/components/modals/UserSettingsModal/Privacy.tsx:179
msgid "When on, senders see when their messages reach your device, and you see when yours reach theirs."
